    "common Pin, Settings, PanelLeft, Search and other geometry was checked against named bundle assets"
  ],
  "policy": [
    "The pinned full family is the only source for ordinary system, navigation, content-action, Settings, status, and capability glyphs.",
    "Adding a new Pige control selects an existing Lucide name and records its semantic mapping here; it does not create a one-off generic SVG.",
    "The prototype subset is an offline-review cache generated from the pinned family, not an independent icon library.",
    "Emoji, text placeholders, arbitrary raw SVG injection, and a second common icon family are prohibited.",
    "Pige brand artwork and a genuinely unique product symbol require a separate UI Design decision and cannot replace a familiar system metaphor.",
    "A Lucide version change requires visual regression of every active mapping at 16, 18, and 20 px before adoption."
  ],
